data.description: Spacious 4 bedroom & 3 bath home in Hoover.  Beautiful home with hardwoods, crown molding, granite kitchen countertops and much more! Master bedroom & bath along with 2 other bedrooms & bath are on the upper floor for added privacy.  Finished basement features an inviting family room with wood burning fireplace, laundry room plus the 4th bedroom and 3rd bath. Large 2 car garage with plenty of storage.  Hoover schools.
